pylapp.tapster.client.android.networks

Class OkHttpClientSkeleton

  • pylapp.tapster.client.android.networks.OkHttpClientSkeleton
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HttpClientStub

    public class OkHttpClientSkeleton
implements HttpClientStub

    Skeleton based on design pattern Bridge which provides the definitions of methods to call so as to deal with networks and HTTP requests. Based on OkHttp library (http://square.github.io/okhttp/)
